Hey HubSpot folks :wave: the example in the docs for “variables in loops” doesn’t work

<https://designers.HubSpot.com/docs/hubl/variables-macros-syntax#variables-within-loops>

I think it should be this:
```  {% set obj = {val : 0} %}
  {% for i in range(0, 10) %}
    {% do obj.update({val: obj.val + i }) %}
  {% endfor %}
  {{ obj.val }}```
